snippet.title: [Official Trailer] “50 Pinch Barrage!!” Port Release Announcement!
snippet.description:
It’s been 10 years since the original version was released for the Nintendo 3DS!
The gameplay is the same but the “Ahhhhh”s are back and more beautiful than ever!
The much-awaited port title “50 Pinch Barrage!!” is coming soon to the Nintendo Switch and Steam!

Genre: Cinematic Pinch-delivering Action
Single player
Languages: English, Japanese, Chinese
Release date: Early Summer 2024
Price: TBA

#50PinchBarrage #50Pinch #pinch50 #pinchbarrage #barragepinch

-----
“50 Pinch Barrage!!” official website (JP only):
https://www.gamestudio.co.jp/pinch50/

“50 Pinch Barrage!!” Steam Store (currently JP only)
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2831540/50/

“50 Pinch Barrage!!” Official X Account (JP):
https://x.com/pinch50

“50 Pinch Barrage!!” Official TikTok Account (JP):
https://www.tiktok.com/@pinch_50
